{\rtf1\ansi \deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss .VnArial;}}{\colortbl;\red0\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;}\deftab720\plain \f0 \fs28 \b \pard\qc \sl280 Ch\'f7a tr\'de b\'d6nh ho t\'b9i nh\'b5 ra sao\plain \f0 \fs26 \par (Thanh ni\'aan )\par \pard\sl260 \par Ho l\'b5 ph\'b6n x\'b9 c\'f1a c\'ac th\'d3 tr\'ad\'edc nh\'f7ng t\'b8c nh\'a9n, k\'ddch th\'ddch \'eb v\'efng h\'c7u, h\'e4ng, thanh qu\'b6n, kh\'dd qu\'b6n, ph\'e6i. Ho g\'e5m ba giai \'aeo\'b9n:\par - H\'ddt v\'b5o: Kh\'abng kh\'dd ngo\'b5i m\'abi tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'ada v\'b5o ph\'e6i.\par - N\'d0n: Thanh m\'abn \'ae\'e3ng l\'b9i - n\'d0n kh\'abng kh\'dd t\'b9i ph\'e6i.\par - Tr\'f4c xu\'cat: Thanh m\'abn m\'eb ra \'ae\'d3 cho lu\'e5ng kh\'abng kh\'dd m\'b9nh th\'e6i qua. Lu\'e5ng kh\'abng kh\'dd n\'b5y c\'e3 t\'e8c \'ae\'e9 t\'e8i \'aea khi qua c\'b8c ph\'d5 qu\'b6n v\'b5 kh\'dd qu\'b6n. Do t\'e8c \'ae\'e9 cao c\'f1a kh\'abng kh\'dd m\'b5 ho c\'e3 th\'d3 t\'e8ng c\'b8c ch\'cat \'ae\'eam d\'b7i v\'b5 d\'de v\'cbt ra ngo\'b5i. Ch\'ddnh giai \'aeo\'b9n n\'b5y ph\'b8t ra \'a9m thanh ta g\'e4i l\'b5 ho.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \b \pard\fi-360 \li360 \sl260 \'b7\tab C\'b8c th\'d3 l\'a9m s\'b5ng c\'f1a ho:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \pard\sl260 - Ho khan, kh\'abng kh\'b9c \'ae\'eam hay g\'c6p trong l\'f3c vi\'aam ph\'e6i ch\'eet ph\'b8t, ung th\'ad ph\'e6i, vi\'aam thanh qu\'b6n.\par - Ho c\'e3 \'ae\'eam: th\'ad\'eang g\'c6p trong vi\'aam h\'e4ng, vi\'aam ph\'d5 qu\'b6n, gi\'b7n ph\'d5 qu\'b6n. Ho c\'acn hay ho ki\'d3u ho g\'b5: g\'c6p trong kh\'e8i u ch\'ccn \'d0p trung th\'cat, hen.\par - Ho hai gi\'e4ng hay r\'df r\'cc: khi lo\'d0t thanh qu\'b6n, li\'d6t thanh qu\'b6n.\par - Ho c\'e3 k\'ccm theo n\'abn: th\'ad\'eang g\'c6p trong tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep d\'a9y th\'c7n kinh X b\'de k\'ddch th\'ddch\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \b \pard\fi-360 \li360 \sl260 \'b7\tab T\'b8c d\'f4ng c\'f1a ho:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \pard\sl260 L\'eei:\par - Qu\'d0t s\'b9ch \'ae\'eam d\'b7i v\'b5 c\'b8c ch\'cat ti\'d5t trong kh\'dd \'ae\'b9o ra ngo\'b5i.\par - T\'e8ng c\'b8c d\'de v\'cbt b\'de r\'aci v\'b5o \'ae\'ad\'eang th\'eb.\par H\'b9i: trong th\'d3 ho khan, kh\'abng kh\'b9c \'ae\'eam n\'e3 g\'e3p ph\'c7n reo gi\'bec c\'b8c b\'d6nh truy\'d2n nhi\'d4m; l\'b5m t\'a8ng \'b8p l\'f9c \'eb ti\'d3u tu\'c7n ho\'b5n; l\'b5m r\'e8i lo\'b9n gi\'cac ng\'f1 v\'b5 l\'b5m cho c\'b8c b\'d6nh nh\'a9n ki\'d6t s\'f8c. \'a7\'abi khi c\'dfn l\'b5m tho\'b8t v\'de c\'ac ho\'b5nh.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \b \pard\fi-360 \li360 \sl260 \'b7\tab C\'e3 nhi\'d2u l\'fd do g\'a9y ra ho:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i \pard\sl260 1/Vi\'aam \'ae\'ad\'eang h\'ab h\'cap tr\'aan:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 - Vi\'aam h\'c7u: hay g\'c6p \'eb ng\'ad\'eai h\'f3t thu\'e8c l\'b8.\par -Vi\'aam thanh qu\'b6n: b\'d6nh b\'b9ch h\'c7u \'eb tr\'ce em. D\'de \'f8ng \'eb ng\'ad\'eai l\'edn, tr\'ce em.\par - Vi\'aam Amydalss ho\'c6c vi\'aam V.A\par - Vi\'aam xoang.\par - Vi\'aam m\'f2i, vi\'aam tai c\'f2ng c\'e3 th\'d3 g\'a9y ho theo ph\'b6n x\'b9.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i 2/C\'b8c b\'d6nh ph\'e6i - m\'b5ng ph\'e6i:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 - Vi\'aam ph\'d5 qu\'b6n c\'cap: do vi tr\'efng ho\'c6c si\'aau vi tr\'efng.\par - Vi\'aam ph\'d5 qu\'b6n m\'b9n: h\'f3t thu\'e8c l\'b8, c\'b8c b\'d6nh ngh\'d2 nghi\'d6p nh\'ad nhi\'d4m b\'f4i ph\'e6i.\par - Vi\'aam ph\'e6i do vi tr\'efng.\par - Lao ph\'e6i.\par - Ung th\'ad ph\'e6i, ung th\'ad v\'efng trung th\'cat.\par - Ung th\'ad m\'b5ng ph\'e6i, lao m\'b5ng ph\'e6i\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i 3/C\'b8c b\'d6nh tim m\'b9ch:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 - Suy tim: nguy\'aan nh\'a9n th\'ad\'eang g\'c6p.\par - T\'bec m\'b9ch ph\'e6i g\'a9y nh\'e5i m\'b8u \'eb ph\'e6i.\par - Ph\'d7nh \'ae\'e9ng m\'b9ch ch\'f1.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i 4/Ho do nguy\'aan nh\'a9n th\'c7n kinh:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \'eb m\'e9t c\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai do nguy\'aan nh\'a9n gi\'cbt c\'ac ng\'ben (tic) c\'f2ng c\'e3 th\'d3 g\'a9y ho.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \b \ul \pard\fi-360 \li360 \sl260 \'b7\tab \'a7i\'d2u tr\'de\plain \f0 \fs26 \b :\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i \pard\sl260 1/M\'e9t s\'e8 b\'b5i thu\'e8c d\'a9n t\'e9c:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 - T\'bec ch\'adng \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'ccn\par - Rau t\'c7n d\'b5y l\'b8 gi\'b7 v\'bet n\'ad\'edc cho v\'b5o \'ddt mu\'e8i \'ae\'d3 u\'e8ng.\par - S\'f3c mi\'d6ng v\'edi n\'ad\'edc mu\'e8i lo\'b7ng\par - \'a1n l\'dfng heo x\'b5o ngh\'d6 v\'b5 h\'d1 ho\'c6c u\'e8ng n\'ad\'edc gi\'b8 tr\'f4ng.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i 2/ Ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p \'aei\'d2u tr\'de T\'a9y y:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 - Ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p v\'cbt l\'fd:\par + X\'abng h\'e4ng b\'bbng h\'aci n\'ad\'edc ng\'b5y v\'b5i l\'c7n.\par + Kh\'dd dung: d\'efng m\'b8y phun s\'ad\'acng \'ae\'ada thu\'e8c v\'b5o s\'a9u trong h\'c7u, h\'e4ng, xoang.\par + S\'f3c mi\'d6ng b\'bbng n\'ad\'edc s\'b8t tr\'efng: Listerine, Seplol.\par - D\'efng thu\'e8c:\par C\'b8c thu\'e8c tr\'de ho g\'e5m 3 nh\'e3m;\par + C\'b8c thu\'e8c \'f8c ch\'d5 trung t\'a9m h\'ab h\'cap: efferagancodein; Dextro methorphan\par + C\'b8c thu\'e8c long \'ae\'eam: Encalyptine, Bisolvon; Terpinzoat Terpingonon. Poterpine.\par + C\'b8c thu\'e8c d\'b7n  ph\'d5 qu\'b6n: Theophyline; Broncho-Soplumux.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i \pard\fi-360 \li360 \sl260 \'b7\tab Ch\'f3 \'fd khi d\'efng thu\'e8c \'ae\'d3 \'aei\'d2u tr\'de ho:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \pard\sl260 + C\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'e8 ho \'ae\'d2u g\'a9y bu\'e5n ng\'f1 nh\'d1 n\'aan th\'cbn tr\'e4ng khi \'ae\'d2u khi\'d3n xe.\par + D\'efng qu\'b8 li\'d2u s\'cf g\'a9y suy h\'ab h\'cap.\par + N\'d5u ch\'c6n ho qu\'b8 s\'edm b\'bbng c\'b8c lo\'b9i thu\'e8c \'f8c ch\'d5 trung t\'a9m h\'ab h\'a9p, \'ae\'eam d\'b7i b\'de \'f8 \'ae\'e4ng, b\'d6nh k\'d0o d\'b5i.\par + C\'c7n k\'d5t h\'eep v\'edi vi\'d6u \'aei\'d2u tr\'de nguy\'aan nh\'a9n.\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i \pard\fi-360 \li360 \sl260 \'b7\tab \'a7\'d3 \'ae\'d2 ph\'dfng c\'b8c b\'d6nh vi\'aam \'ae\'ad\'eang h\'ab h\'cap:\par \plain \f0 \fs26 \pard\sl260 +Tr\'b8nh thay \'ae\'e6i m\'abi tr\'ad\'eang qu\'b8 \'ae\'e9t ng\'e9t: ra v\'b5o ph\'dfng l\'b9nh qu\'b8 th\'ad\'eang xuy\'aan.\par + Kh\'abng h\'f3t thu\'e8c l\'b8.\par + Khi c\'e3 hi\'d6n t\'ad\'eeng ho: c\'c7n gi\'f7 \'cam c\'e6, kh\'abng u\'e8ng n\'ad\'edc qu\'b8 n\'e3ng, qu\'b8 l\'b9nh\par \par \plain \f0 \fs26 \i \par \plain \f0 \fs26 \par \plain \f0 \fs26 \b \par \plain \f0 \fs20 \par }